{"talk":{"id":63318,"name":"Anne Basting: How to meaningfully reconnect with those who have dementia","description":"By incorporating art and creativity into elder care settings, gerontologist Anne Basting helps families reconnect with loved ones who have dementia. In this moving talk, she shares how asking \"beautiful questions\" -- questions that don't have a right or wrong answer -- opens up a shared path of discovery, imagination and wonder. \"If we can infuse creativity into care, caregivers can invite a partner into meaning-making,\" Basting says. \"In that moment, care, which is so often associated with loss, can become generative.\"","slug":"anne_basting_how_to_meaningfully_reconnect_with_those_who_have_dementia","recorded_at":"2020-03-04 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-05-21 15:02:42","updated_at":"2020-11-28 12:10:30","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":643,"name":"TEDMED 2020"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/422e1ebc89bff6d69b89389bca36c99180ec8bbf_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/422e1ebc89bff6d69b89389bca36c99180ec8bbf_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/422e1ebc89bff6d69b89389bca36c99180ec8bbf_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/422e1ebc89bff6d69b89389bca36c99180ec8bbf_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/d2875521fe05baf824d951a72999665a80ee765a_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AnneBasting_2020P-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7304140,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AnneBasting_2020P-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":20249768,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AnneBasting_2020P-320k.mp4?ap